@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: Collaborate

actor User
participant "ControllerInput Manager" as Input
participant "HUD" as HUD
participant "Collaboration Manager" as Colab
participant "Security Manager" as Auth
participant "Network Manager" as Network
participant "Room Manager" as Room
participant "CanvasSpawner" as Spawner
participant "CanvasBrushSpawner" as BrushSpawner
participant "Art Tools (BrushToolState)" as Tools
participant "Canvas (PaintableSurfaceRT)" as Canvas
participant "CanvasStrokeSyncNgo" as StrokeSync
participant "Event Logger" as Logger

== User Joins a Shared Workspace ==
User -> Input: Selects "Join a workspace"
Logger -> Logger: Log SelectsJoinWorkspace
Input -> HUD: Display code textbox
User -> Input: Inputs code
Input -> HUD: Submits code
Logger -> Logger: Log code
HUD -> Colab: Validates code
Colab -> Auth: Sends user info
Auth --> Colab: Authenticates user
Colab -> Network: Load workspace instance
Logger -> Logger: Log workspace info
Network -> Room: Load workspace layout
Room -> Canvas: Load artworks (SetBackground → Graphics.Blit to RenderTexture)

== Brush & Canvas Spawn (on workspace load) ==
Room -> Spawner: SpawnWorkspaceServerRpc(pos, rot)
activate Spawner
Spawner -> Spawner: Instantiate workspace prefab
Spawner -> Spawner: NetworkObject.Spawn()
Spawner -> BrushSpawner: SpawnBrush()
BrushSpawner -> BrushSpawner: Instantiate paintbrush prefab at canvas offset
BrushSpawner -> Network: NetworkObject.Spawn() — brush visible to all clients
deactivate Spawner

== User Collaborates on a Painting ==
User -> Input: Selects canvas (walks up / ray points)
Logger -> Logger: Log canvas selected
Input -> Canvas: Zoom in (enter draw mode)

User -> Input: Picks up brush (XR grab)
Input -> Tools: BrushGrabState.OnGrabbed()
Tools -> BrushSpawner: RequestReplacementBrushServerRpc() — spawn replacement for others
Tools -> HUD: Show current brush color/radius

loop While trigger held (every frame)
    User -> Input: Pull trigger, move controller
    Input -> Input: Physics.Raycast() → hit.textureCoord (UV)
    Input -> Tools: GetHeldBrushToolState() → BrushState (color, radius, hardness)
    Input -> StrokeSync: LocalStrokeBegin(strokeId, brushState) [first frame]
    Input -> Canvas: TryPaintAt(uv, brushState)
    Canvas -> Canvas: Graphics.Blit(BufferA → BufferB, brushBlitMaterial)
    Canvas -> Canvas: Swap buffers (ping-pong)
    Canvas -> Canvas: ApplyToRenderer(BufferA)
    Input -> StrokeSync: LocalStrokePoints(strokeId, encodedUVs)
    StrokeSync -> Network: BroadcastStroke RPC to all clients
    Network --> Canvas: Remote clients paint same stroke
end

User -> Input: Release trigger
Input -> StrokeSync: LocalStrokeEnd(strokeId)
StrokeSync -> Network: Finalise stroke sync

== User Saves Artwork ==
User -> HUD: Click Save Artwork
HUD -> Canvas: SaveCanvasToPNG(fileName)
Canvas -> Canvas: Texture2D.ReadPixels(RenderTexture)
Canvas -> Canvas: tex.EncodeToPNG()
Canvas --> HUD: Return localPath

note over StrokeSync, Network
    CanvasStrokeSyncNgo handles all NGO RPCs.
    No per-stroke auth call — auth happens at join time.
    BrushRespawnOnGrab auto-despawns idle brushes after timeout.
end note

== User Messages Another User ==
User -> Input: Selects chat
Logger -> Logger: Log Chat selected
Input -> HUD: Display chat
User -> Input: Enters message
Input -> HUD: Saves message
Logger -> Logger: Log Message
HUD -> Colab: Send message
Colab -> Network: Broadcast to room

@enduml
